question.query: What defi protocols have the best valuation (P/S)?

steps.text:
Do you mean token/project Price-to-Sales (market cap ÷ protocol revenue, usually trailing-12m) for DeFi protocols and want the lowest P/S (i.e., “cheapest” by P/S)? 

If so:
- How many protocols do you want ranked (top 10, top 20, full list)?
- Any preferred data source? (Token Terminal is the standard for on‑chain P/S; CoinGecko shows some Token Terminal metrics too.)
- Do you want circulating‑market‑cap P/S or fully‑diluted P/S?

I can pull the latest ranked list and a short summary once you confirm.
